te phase diagram of SmFe1-xNixAsO (x = 0.0 to\n1.0) is studied in terms of its structural, electrical, magnetic and thermal\nproperties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Sep 2012 05:11:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Nov 2012 08:16:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 6 Dec 2012 08:08:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
