 solutions is also\nstudied. It turns out that some quite different phenomena appear comparing to\nthe special case N=4.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Sep 2012 08:47:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Aug 2013 12:35:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
