 are\nbroadly applicable and may help solve the missing heritability problem in\ncomplex traits and diseases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Sep 2012 06:30:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Jul 2013 02:17:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-04"}
